text:
Flushing Airport (Queens): A view southeastward toward the airport, seen from 129th Street near 15th Avenue, College Point. The airport is situated between Flushing and College Point.

P. L. Sperr

View 1: March 3, 1932
View 2: April 13, 1937

View 2: The area that later became the Flushing Airport.
title: Airports - Flushing Airport - Queens.
